   3.575551781664343*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a7fe33f-412f-4e0b-9cf0-\
75344edad8de"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " allows calculations in a space of orthogonal spin operators, known as ",
 StyleBox["Liouville space. ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.57435106157069*^9, 
  3.574351086978191*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"05ab7484-886d-4d08-925a-\
643f0f7ecc27"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["LiouvilleBracket", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.574351105440606*^9, 
  3.574351112824636*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8a7394cc-f282-4ec5-a6eb-\
a140069e7caa"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In Liouville space, the scalar product of two operators is known as the \
Liouville bracket, and is calculated as follows: (A|B) = Tr",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SuperscriptBox["A", "\[Dagger]"], "B"}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"e1c28231-c49b-4a93-87c3-73bf835a79a1"],
 ", where Tr is the trace, and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["A", "\[Dagger]"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0e1f79aa-93ca-4928-a14f-c747fde89dea"],
 " is the adjoint of ",
 "A. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.57435112683681*^9, 3.574351208180372*^9}, {
  3.574351260324024*^9, 
  3.5743513049366426`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"08816c7b-5f0c-4342-a4bf-\
e6f54098e3b2"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In ",
 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " the Liouville bracket of two operators is calculated using ",
 StyleBox["LiouvilleBracket",
  FontWeight->"Bold"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.574351310109919*^9, 3.57435132864797*^9}, {
  3.5743513606391582`*^9, 
  3.574351363007905*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7be83763-3e4f-4258-acf6-\
b6c922de3644"],

