Cell["\<\
This basis is sorted in default \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]canonical\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] order, meaning that the first ket in the Zeeman \
basis is combined with all bras, then the second ket is combined with all \
bras, and so on, until all ket.bra combinations have been generated.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5743516970890927`*^9, 3.574351741274046*^9}, {
  3.574351875818799*^9, 3.574351885699317*^9}, {3.574352399551989*^9, 
