Cell["\<\
In this case, all possible operators for spin #1 are multiplied by the first \
operator for spin #2, followed by all possible operators for spin #1 \
multiplied by the second operator for spin #2, and so on, until all \
combinations are generated. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.574352688702378*^9, 3.574352763940035*^9}, {
  3.574352819365652*^9, 
  3.574352842131711*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f321b83d-b09a-47fb-bc18-\
