Cell[TextData[{
 "CartesianProductOperatorBasis",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "is also defined for systems of spins > 1/2. However the combinations of \
operators leading to an orthogonal basis is not intuitive in this case. The \
example below is for a single spin-3/2:"
}], "Text",
