Cell["\<\
Superoperators generate a linear transformation of an operator into another \
operator. SpinDynamica supports a set of common superoperator types.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.546621565515342*^9, 3.546621578478991*^9}, {
  3.5466216241115522`*^9, 3.546621662997705*^9}, {3.5743158814299097`*^9, 
  3.574315914743665*^9}, {3.574316613019311*^9, 
  3.574316620793651*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"97a82b89-cb89-4183-a582-\
a3e6307bf44c"],

Cell["\<\
The matrix representation of a superoperator in a particular operator basis \
is generated using SuperoperatorMatrixRepresentation. Examples are given \
below. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.575554314016124*^9, 
  3.575554327553857*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bfcb7f14-6411-49e6-93de-\
f67aa088ef43"],

