Cell["\<\
Left and RightMultiplicationSuperoperators may be defined through the use of \
LeftMultiplicationSuperoperator[op] and RightMultiplicationSuperoperator[op]. 

Left and RightMultplicationSuperoperators multiply their operator argument \
from the left and right, respectively.\
\>", "Text",
